<li>This code does not work in <span class="bbcode-verbatim">[pywindow]</span>.</li>
<li>You cannot access the contents of the tab you are running the code in while it is running, so remember to memorize the target username before running the code.</li>
<li>You can rerun the code once it has finished running.</li>
<li>You can run the code even if you have a reply partly written.</li>
